-
I kitea te rētō o ngā puna pūmanawa o ngā toa whutuporo me raro i te 18 tau te pakeke o ngā Chiefs me ngā Blues i te rangi nei i tauronarona ki St Pauls Collegiate.
-
Ka whakanui te toki Chiefs a Hikawera Elliot i tētahi ekenga nui kotahi rau takaro i te Super Rugby ki tōna kapa o mua.
-
Nō te rā nei ka puta te uri o Ngāti Awa, a Ben Afeaki, ka whakairi i ana hū takaro, nā ngā raru hauora te take.
-
He pō pouri mā te kapa Blues, i hinga i tā rātou tukinga tuawhitu o ngā tukinga e whitu i te whakataetae Super Rugby, heoi he tukinga pai mā te kapa Chiefs, i wikitōria i te tukinga me te piki whakarunga ki te turanga tuawhā o te tēpu whakataetae me ngā wikitōria e ono i ngā tukinga e waru.
-

Kaore te waikura parahi e waikura, kaore hoki e rereke te tae i nga wera nui, na te pai o te kawe i ngawari ai te pani ki etahi atu taputapu. Ko te pepa parahi i hangaia e te mahinga hiko he tino ma te papa me te ahua o tetahi pepa papa. Ko te pepa parahi ano ka paruparu tetahi taha, maamaa ai te piri atu ki etahi atu rawa. ...

Katapere.

... 
ga ture o te Kuini i whakatupu tangata ai ratou."
Muri iho ka puta to ratou tohu aroha ki nga Pakeha "o te kainga e tauria nei e te pouritanga, a Taranaki." Ka rongo hoki ratou, ka mate nga Pakeha i te rawa kore, kua pau hoki nga taonga i te pahua: ki te whakaaro hoki o o ratou hoa Pakeha kia kawea ki Katapere etahi o nga koroheke, wahine, tamatriki,—e kohikohi ana i te moni mo tera; ka mea ano nga Maori ma ratou hoki tetahi wahi o tera kohikohinga. Na, kua kohikohi a Kaiapoi 10l. 14s, a Rapaki 
...
, ka mea e haere pea ki Taranaki ki page 3 te iwi e whawhai ana, ka pouri ratou mo tenei, ka hiahia ano kia karangatia tetahi hui, e puta rawa ai o ratou whakaaro ki nga taringa o nga Pakeha kia kaua ai ratou e pera. Kua whakaae ano nga kai-whakariterite o nga Pakeha ki tenei, mea ana, hei te 13 o nga ra o Hepitema whakaturia ai he runanga mo te Pakeha mo te Maori, ki Otautahi, hei whakakotahitanga i nga iwi e rua, kia whakatupu tuakana, teina, ki runga o te aroha, ki runga o te ture o te Kuini.

Pānui
Pānuitia ngā kōrero e whai ake nei, kātahi ka whakautu ai i ngā pātai.
He kōrerorero
Kei te toa a Tarati rāua ko Wiremu e hoko kai ana, ka tūtaki rāua i a Mīria rāua ko Te Hererīpene.
Wiremu: Kei te haere au ki te tiki torore.
Tarati: Āe, me haere au ki te wāhi huawhenua. Kia tere!
Ka pānui a Tarati i ngā rārangi kai e hiahiatia ana i a Wiremu e tiki atu ana i te torore.
Tarati: Wiremu, tīkina atu ngā ārani.
Wiremu: Kia hia?
Tarati: Kia rua ngā pēke.
Wiremu: Āe, kei te pīrangi āporo hoki?
Tarati: Āe, tīkina atu kia tekau ngā āporo.
Ka tatau a Tarati rāua ko Wiremu i ngā āporo, “Ka tahi, ka rua, ka toru, ka whā, ka …” Ka kitea rāua e Mīria rāua ko Te Hererīpene.
Mīria: Tēnā kōrua.
Tarati: Tēnā kōrua. Kei te pēhea kōrua?
Mīria: Kei te kaha tonu.
Te Hererīpene: Heoi anō. Kei te pēhea tō whānau, Wiremu?
Wiremu: Kei te pērā tonu.
Mīria: Kei te pīrangi kōrua ko tō whānau ki te haere mai ki taku whare?
Wiremu: Ki te aha, e kui?
Mīria: Ki te kai, ki te kōrero hoki.
Tarati: E kāo. Me haere kē mai kōrua ki tō māua kāinga.
Mīria: Āna. Me hari mai au i te aha?
Wiremu: Kei te pai, e kui. Kāore kau.
Mīria: He keke pea?
Tarati: Āe, ka rawe, e kui. Ka kite māua i a koe ā te pō nei.
Mīria: Āna, e noho rā kōrua.
Wiremu: Āe, hei konā rā.

E whai ana ngā hua rangahau nei i tā te kāwanatanga i oati ai, ka whakahekea kē ngā tukunga mā te rima ōrau i mua i te ekenga ki taua tau.

I aha i noho taonga ai te kōura?
Ko Aotearoa anake te kāinga tūturu o te kōura wai māori (ko te kēwai anō tētahi o ōna ingoa). E rua ngā momo:
- Ko Paranephrops planifrons – kei Te Ika-a-Māui me Te Tai Poutini (arā, te tai hau-ā-uru o Te Waipounamu)
- Ko Paranephrops zealandicus – kei te taha rāwhiti me te taha tonga o Te Waipounamu.
Ko te kōura tētahi o ngā ika tuatahi, ngā ika taketake o Aotearoa. Nō tua whakarere ōna kāwai whakapapa. Nō te takiwā o te 109-60 mirio
... 
ahi tonu te kōura i Rotoiti, i Rotomā, i Tarawera (i Te Moana-a-Toi) me Taupō (i te rohe o Waikato).
He kawenga nui tā te kōura i te pūnaha hauropi wai māori. He kai pai mā ētahi atu ika māori pēnei i te tuna (ngā momo Anguilla), i te kōkopu (Galaxias argenteus), i te īnanga (Galaxias maculatus), i te pōrohe (Retropinna retropinna), mā ētahi manu māori hoki pērā i te kawau (ngāi Phalacrocorax) ā, mā te tangata anō. He kai ota, he kai kiko te kōura, he kai toenga whakapopo anō. He tūranga nui tōn

Me pēhea te mahi paura miraka?
Āta pānuihia ngā mōhiohio kei te tini paura miraka (tae ki te rā mōnehu) ka whai i ngā tohutohu. Me mātua whakamahi i te koko kei roto i te tini.
Āta pānuihia ngā mōhiohio kei te tini paura miraka (tae ki te rā mōnehu) ka whai i ngā tohutohu. Me mātua whakamahi i te koko kei roto i te tini.
Ehara te paura miraka pēpi i te horomata. Āta whakamahi me te putu paura miraka kia noho pai ai mō te pēpi.
Me whakarite te paura miraka i mua tonu i te whāngainga.
Ki te kore e taea, ka taea te waiho i te paura miraka kua whakaritea ki te pāmahana ā-whare atu ki te 2 haora te roa, ki rō pouaka makariri atu ki te 4 haora te roa.
Mō ngā marama e 3 tuatahi o tō pēpi, me paera ngā wai katoa ka whakamātao i te rā ka whakamahia e koe.
I ngā tāone nui me ngā tāone, ka taea e koe te whakamahi wai mai i te kōrere wai hei mahi paura miraka i muri i te ekenga ki te 3 marama. Atu i tēnā, me paera haere tonu te wai.

TE WHAKAMAHI
- Whakapaa atu ki to kaiwhakaari arotahi mo te whakahaunga, i mua i te whakamahi i nga rongoa kanohi i a koe e mau ana i nga karaahe whakapiri.
- Kaua e whakamahia ki te pakaru te hiri taapiri-kitea.
- I roto i te kaupapa e ngau ana te kanohi, ka mutu te whakamahi i te manawaateley, tangohia te tirohanga mai i te kanohi me te korero ki to kaimahi tirotiro whakapakarihia.
- Kia mau tonu nga taonga tiaki arotahi ki nga tamariki.
- Kaua e tango i te potae mai i te keehi i te rokiroki arotahi whakapā.
- Kaua e tukua te matamata o te nozzle kia pa ki tetahi mata.
- Whakakapihia nga potae pounamu i muri i te whakamahinga.
- Kaua e tarai i nga arotahi whakapiri he keehi ranei ki te wai totika mai i te paato.
- Kei te hiahia koe i tetahi whakaaetanga mai i tetahi tohunga mo te arotahi whakapiri hei whakamahi i enei karaihe whakapiri.
- Ko to keehi rokiroki arotahi me horoi tonu i nga wa katoa ka hurihia i runga i te taunakitanga a to kaiwhakaari ki nga pukoro whakapiri.
- Kia kore ai e ea te haumaru kanohi, kaua e whakamahia e koe te otinga. Mena he rongoa neke atu i te 7 nga ra i roto i te otinga, ka taunakihia kia whakahouhia e koe te mahinga patu.
- Kaua e whakamahia i muri i te ra paunga e tohua ana ki te hua.

Ko ngā hua o Hiwa-i-te-rangi i puta ki te kapa Northern Stars i tō rātau wikitōria tuatahi o tēnei whatinga.
I pakanga ngā Stars mō te hemo tonu atu e tutuki ai te wawata, ā, whakapaua katoatia ai te kaha e toa ai i a rātau te hauwhā tuatahi e whitu piro ki mua.
Hoki mai ai te kapa Tactix ki te hauwhā tuarua anō he mate e rānakihia ana, me te aha, i kapi haere te tatauranga piro. Heoi anō, nā te panonitanga o te uri tāroaroa o Ngāpuhi, o Holly Fowler hai poka pū me te arotahi a te kāpene, a Grace Kara ki ana kaitukituki, i kānapa tonu ai te kapa Stars.
Kitea ai te pakanga o roto i te kapa Tactix i te hāwhe tuarua, i te huhua o ngā haukotinga o ngā kaikaupare, o Temalisi Fakahokotau rāua ko Jane Watson. Ko Kimiora Poi hoki tērā i manaaki i te poi ki te taha tukituki, me te aha, kapi ana i te kapa Tactix ngā tatauranga ki te piro kotahi i ngā miniti whakamutunga o te tukinga.
Kati ai te kēmu, ko ngā Stars kai runga, e rima-tekau-mā-ono ki te rima-tekau-mā-toru. Hai te rauna tuawaru tuki ai rātau ki ngā puru rourou o te whakataetae, ki te kapa Pulse.

He aha te miraka kahore-paturopi?
Kao- te miraka paturopi e whakaarohia ana mo te waiu kei roto he paturopi. Ko te miraka kore-paturopi, e kii ana te ingoa, ko te miraka kaore he paturopi. Ko te miraka i hua mai i te miraka kau noa me te kore he paturopi he "no- antibiotic milk". Ehara i te momo momo miraka engari ko te korero mo te miraka kaore he paturopi. Te miraka ranei me nga "toenga paturopi kaore i kitea". Ko tenei waa e mohiotia ana e te nuinga o te iwi, engari kaore e kitea i roto i nga
... 
 i te miraka mata, kia mohio ai ko te miraka "Guangming" kei te maakete "nga hua katoa kaore he paturopi". Mai i tenei tirohanga, e hiahia ana ki te whakangao i nga utu whaainga kau, kia ora ai nga hua miraka. Ko te utu mo te whakamahi i nga "hua katoa kaore he awangawanga" ko nga umanga me utu i nga utu mo te whakamatautau, te whiwhi me te whakahaere, te whakangungu me te tirotiro.
Ko nga aitua matū pēnei i te toenga paturopi i te miraka e ahu mai ana i nga waahanga e wha: te rongoa o nga kau w
...

Ko te Piko Taha Barbell he whakangungu whakangungu kaha e aro nui ana ki nga uaua tapapa, ki te whakaniko i te tino pumau me te whakapai ake i te kaha o te tinana. He pai mo te hunga timata me te hunga kaingākau ki te whakapakari tinana na te mea ka ngawari te whakarereke kia rite ki nga taumata whakapakari tinana takitahi. Ka hiahia nga tangata ki te mahi i tenei mahi hei whakarei ake i o raatau kaha matua, whakapai ake i o raatau tuuranga, me te tautoko i o raatau oranga tinana me o raatau whaainga taumaha.
Ae, ka taea e te hunga timata te mahi i te korikori Piko Taha Barbell, engari he mea nui kia timata ma te taumaha kia kore e whara me te whakarite kia tika te ahua. Ko tenei mahi ko te tino aro ki nga uaua tapapa i nga taha o to puku. He mea nui ki te pupuri i te mana whakahaere me te kore e tuku i te taumaha kia tere rawa koe ki raro. Pērā i ngā mahi korikori tinana, me whai whakaaro te hunga tīmata ki te tiki tohutohu mai i te tohunga ngaio tinana kia tika ai, kia haumaru hoki te mahi.

Ko te faimalaga ki Niu Hila
Ka malaga koe ki Niu Hila, e iei na manakoga e tatau ke fakatino muamua e koe.
Ko na vaega ka taku atu ko na fakamaoniga e tatau ke ia te koe ka ulu atu koe ki Niu Hila.
Kua he manakomia e koe he pepa hiakiga mo tau malaga ke malaga ai ki Niu Hila. E he manakomia ke fai o tui puipui, pe fai ho hiakiga ka taunuku koe ki Niu Hila.
E mafai ke vave lele ni huiga - Immigration New Zealand e kilatou tukua atu ni fakamatalaga fou.
1. HIaki muamua ko koe e mafai ke malaga mai
... 
.
Ka ko heki malaga koe, fakamautinoa ko tau passport e lelei ke malaga ai koe. E ia manakomia foki koe ke apalai kihe New Zealand Electronic Travel Authority (NZeTA).
2. Fakatonu ho avanoa malaga
Fakatonu ho avanoa malaga ki Niu Hila.
Hiaki te polihi mo na tui ma na malaga kua fakaheai ma kilatou e malaga ai koe na teki e hui au peleni.
E tatau ke mafaufau koe ke iei hau travel insurance na teki kua afaina pe hui na peleni. E tatau ke iei he fale ke nofo kehe ai koe na teki atu e manakomia.
3. 
...
iketi mo tau faigamalaga
6. Taunukuga ki Niu Hila
E fakamaonia e te Customs au femalagaakiga ma ho he tahi manakoga ke ulufale ai koe. E mafai ke tuai malie koe i te malae vakalele.
E maua na Afifiga feiloaki i te Biosecurity ka taumuku mai koe. Te afifiga feiloaki tenei e iei ai:
- na heti hiakiga vave o te anetiteni (RAT)
- taki mo na hukehukega ma te tuku atuga o tau lipoti ki te neti.
E fautuagia ke fakataunuku te fakatinoga o au hukehukega ma tuku te lipoti tena ki te neti.

Ko Rota Waitoa te Māori tuatahi o te hāhi Mihinare i iriiritia e te mihinare e Octavius Hadfield ki Waikanae i te tau 1841. E ai ki te kaiārahi hapori a Kahurangi Martin, 'he tangata pakihiwi nui, mata nui, harakoa hoki ia, anō nei tōna āhua he Awherikana' (Ann Martin, Our Māoris. London: Society for Promoting Christian Knowledge, 1884, p. 175). Whai muri i tona whakawāhinga i te tau 1853 ka tū ia hei minita ki Te Araroa i te Tai Rāwhiti i te wā e ngaro haere ana te awe o ngā mihinare Pākehā ki waenganui i te Māori. Ka ātete ia i te Kīngitanga, ā, ka tū hoki ia ki ngā pakanga ki ngā Hauhau ki te Tai Rāwhiti i te tau 1865.

E tono nei a Tā Toby Curtis mātanga mātauranga kia tere te ū o te kereme Wai 2770 ki mua i te rōpū whakamana i te Tiriti o Waitangi. E hāngai ana te kereme ki te whakakorehanga o ngā kura hōurua. Ko tā Toby e mea ana, he whakaaro takitahi tō te Minita Mātauranga. “Kia tere wā rātou mahi, kia puta mai wa rātou kōrero, i mua i te mahi a te Minita ki te kati i ēnei kura”. Kua tono ngā kura hōurua kia ū ki raro i ngā mārautanga mātauranga. Engāri ki Tā Toby, taihoa. “Kei te hē tērā hiahia, me kati wēnei kura, i mua i te haerehanga ki wēnei kura, kāre rātou i te hiahia ki te haere ki te kura i te mea i pōhēhē rātou karekau wō rātou take”. Tekau mā tahi ngā kura hōurua i whakatūhia ki Aotearoa. Nō te Hui Tangarū i tango te wāhanga i pā ana ki ngā kura hōurua ki roto i te ture mātauranga. “Kua noho wahangū wā tātau mema o te whareparemata, he maha wā tātau mema kei reira, mema Māori, ana kātahi anō tātau ka kite nuinga o ngā Minita Māori i roto i tēnei kāwanatanga. Kāre tētahi kupu e puta mai i a rātou ki te tautoko i wēnei”. E ai ki Te Rōpū Whakamana i te Tiriti o Waitangi, kāre anō kia tau te rā, kia rongohia te kereme ki mua i a rātou.

Engari i tēnei marama o Dry July, kei te whakarite a Ninakaye, kua neke atu i te rua tekau tau e noho pare ana i te waipiro, i tētahi kaupapa kohi pūtea e kī ana ko On The Waka, hei tautoko i ngā pārurenga o te mate pukupuku.
Nāna te kaupapa o ‘On The Waka’ i whakamānu ai mō te hunga e whai ana i te ao waipiro kore, hei āhuru mōwai i ngā piere nuku kei mua i a rātou.
I tāna rangatahitanga ka taka ia ki ngā rāngai toukohi mahi ai, nā tēna ka tau mai ngā taumahatanga o te waipiro me te tarukino.
Nā te rāweke ki ngā warawara o te ao mō ngā tau, ka hinga ia i te hauhauaitū, te pōātinitini me te whakaruhi i te wairangi nā te waipiro me ngā tarukino.
A, i tana hapūtanga tuatahi, ka huri te tai, ka hīnātore mai te māramatanga i tōna hinengaro ki te ara o te tika.
Ka whitawhita mai te ahi i roto i a Taane-Tinorau ki te tautoko i ngā whānau kua pāngia e te mate pukupuku, nā te ngau kino o te ngāngara i tōna whānau.
Hei tā Taane-Tinorau kua penapena tōna toru mano waru rau taara i tēnei wā, ko te whāinga kia eke ki te rima mano.
Ko te manako nui ā 'On The Waka' kia tū hei āhuru mōwai mā ngā mema nei, kia waiho mā ngā whēako rātou e ārahi ki te ao waipiro kore, kaua noaiho mā te marama o Hūrae anake.

faaite Pope Francis konei Rātapu e te muri Day Youth World (WYD), te fest to'u tupú Katorika, ka tū i roto i te pa Polish o Krakow i 2016.
“hoa taitamariki aroha, to tatou he mea whakarite mo te Day World Tupú muri i roto i 2016 i roto i te Krakow, Poland,” ka mea ia i te mutunga o te puranga tae e toru miriona manene i runga i Rio o beach Copacabana.
I tākai Parata-whanau Francis ake he toronga wiki-roa ki Brazil, o tino tini te ao whenua Katorika, i runga i tona haerenga tāwāhi tuatahi mai i tona pōtitanga i Maehe.
Ko te kōwhiringa o Krakow i te honore o John Paul II, nei Rere i Krakow me te hunga tīmata te Day Youth Ao (WYD) ngā i roto i tona papacy mana.
“faaite tatou i to tatou mauruuru ki te E te Matua tapu hoki tenei whakatau,” ka mea a Cardinal Stanisław Dziwisz, te pīhopa tāone o Krakow, i roto i te tauākī tukua konei. “titiro whakamua matou ki tou mai, me te ki te taenga mai o na e rave rahi o to tatou mau hoa taitamariki, ki te anaanatae rahi, me te koa.”
I tū te WYD mōhiohio tuatahi i roto i 1986, ahakoa i mua i te reira e rua huihuinga papatipu o mua o te iwi taitamariki i huri noa i te ao i roto i Roma.
I tū te tau e whai ake nei i roto i te pane Parata te muri Buenos Aires, te wahi i Francis pīhopa i mua riro ia popa.

Whārangi 1: Haurongo
Awatere, Arapeta Marukitepua Pitapitanuiarangi
1910–1976
Nō Ngāti Porou, nō Ngāti Hine; he kaiwhakamāori, he kaingārahu hōia, he āpiha toko i te ora Māori, he kaitōrangapū ā-rohe, he tangata i whiua e te ture mō te kōhuru
I tuhia tēnei haurongo e Hinemoa Ruataupare Awatere,, ā, i tāngia tuatahitia ki Ngā Tāngata Taumata Rau Ko te wāhanga , 2000.
I whānau mai a Arapeta Marukitepua Pitapitanuiārangi Awatere (ko Te Arapeta Pitameirangi Marukitepua Awatere anō te momo tuhi i tōn
... 
a o te ahi. He tangata manawanui a Awatere, he amorangi ki mua, atawhai koretia e ia te hoariri. I hū haere tonu ngā whakapae mō ngā mau herehere e tūkino, e kōhurutia ana. Hoi anō ka mau kē te wehi me te mataku anō o āna tāngata i a ia. I te wā i a rātau e hūhunu haere ana, e whawhai kē ana rānei, whakahautia ana e ia āna tāngata kia kōrero Māori, uhingaro Māori rānei, kia kore ai e mōhio te hoariri e whakarongo ana, e aha ana rātau.
Nō muri i tana hokinga mai ki Aotearoa i Ākuhata o te tau 194
...
hia ana ki te poroporoaki i a ia, ā, ahakoa tā rātau hari i a ia mā huarahi kē, aukatia noatia ana e ētahi te huarahi kia mau ake tā rātau tangi ki a ia i tō rātau marae. Ko Mangahānea, i te rohe o Ngāti Porou, te wāhi takoto whakamutunga mōna, ahakoa te tono a Ngāti Hine kia whakahokia atu ia ki Te Tai Tokerau. Ko ōna hoa tonu o te pakanga i te hiki i a ia. Ēngari i te pikihanga whakamutunga ōna ki Waitetoki, riro kē ana nā ana mokopuna ia i mau atu, ā, nehua ake ana ia ki te taha o tōna whaea.

Ko Lucas McKinnon tētahi o ngā kaiwhakahaere o te whakataetae nei, hei tāna nā Raahui Pookeka te maringanui i whakakao atu te motu ki runga i tō rātou hāpori.
Kī apiapi atu te Whare Ora o te Wharekura o Rākaumanga i ngā karapu kyokushin puta noa i te motu, tae atu ki Illawarra i Ahitereiria.
... 
 ki ngā tikanga e tika ai ana ngā whanonga o ngā tamariki.
Ko Shihan Stephen Takiwa te kanohi kitea mō Aotearoa ki Hāpāni, kua 35 tau ia e whakapeto ngoi ana i ngā mahi kyokushin. Hei tāna, kua piki te nama o ngā karapu mai i te 15 ki te 30. Hei tāna anō, nā te rahi o ngā rangatahi e whakangūngū ana, e piatata rawa ā tau koroī.
Ko te kata tētahi o ngā wahanga o te whakataetae, he wahanga e whakaatu ai ngā kaiwhakataetae i nga nekehanga onamata. Hei tā Shihan Takiwa anō, ka uaua pea mō ngā rangat
...
oki i tētahi kapa hei whakakanohi i ā Aotearoa ki Hāpāni i te tau e heke mai nei. Hei tā Shihan Takiwa, ka tipakohia e rātou i tētahi kapa tāne, ēngari e hiahia hoki ana kia kawea atu i ētahi rangatahi, wāhine me ētahi anō nō te reanga kaumātua.
Ko Lucas McKinnon tētahi kua tae atu ki Hāpāni mō ngā mahi kyokushin. Hei tāna, ka tino kite e te kapa nei i ngā momo ahurea o te ao i a rātou i reira. Ko tāna anō, he ōrite te ahurea Hāpāni ki tā te Māori. Ka mutu, kua horapa katoa te ao i te Kyokushin.

Whangārei-terenga-paraoa
Ko Whangārei-terenga-paraoa, arā ko Te Tauwhanga a Reipae (Whangarei) te tāone nui o Te Tai-tokerau, Te Ika-a-Māui, Aotearoa. Kei raro te tāone nei i te mana o te Kaunihera ā-Rohe o Whangārei, he takiwā i whakatūria i te tau 1989 hei whakahaere i te tāone nui me te rohe whānui. I puta mai te kaunihera nei i ngā kaunihera o mua o Te Tāonenui o Whangārei, Te Kaute o Whangārei me te Tāone o Hikurangi. Nō te 2013, kua tae te taupori ki te 52,900, ake i 47,000 i te tau 2001.

Mass laulima hiki no hoi ke kōkua me ka aeaiiuo ohi, aka, he mea tricky e hamama ai aeaiiuo e like ai, a me systematic hoʻokokoke mai i ka mea hōʻikeʻikeʻuʻuku.
A iâ lâkou e pili ana kanaka hou, a hamama mau kāhea, noiʻi hiki no hoi hana i haawi aeaiiuo ohi papahana. Ma ka oiaio, nui no quantitative nohona 'epekema ano nui ma luna o māhele aeaiiuo ohi i loko o ke ano o ka lawelawe ana ma na limahana. No ka mea, laʻana, e ohi i ka ikepili no ka General Social Survey, he poʻe mea hoolimalima i ka huli hires interviewers ka poe e hele i ka respondent i wahi e ohi i ka ike mai ia lakou. Aka, heaha ina kakou hiki somehow enlist hana manawaleʻa, e like me ikepili ÿauhau?
E like me na hoailona ma lalo, mai ka ornithology, a me kekahi polokalamu kamepiula, 'epekema-hoike puunaue aeaiiuo ohi mau hiʻohiʻona nō noiʻi e ohi i ka ikepili hou aku pinepine ia, a me ka nui wahi mamua, ua hiki mua. Eia, haawi kūpono Hola Pūnaewele, ua 'ike hiki ke ike loea lawa ia e hoʻohana no ka' epekema noiʻi. In mea, no ka mea, kekahi noiʻi ninau, haawi aeaiiuo haul, uaʻoi aku ma mua o kekahi mea i makemake realistically e hiki no ia i uku ia ikepili ÿauhau.

Whiriwhiringia
Tuhinga o mua Whiriwhiringia hangaia e te he kowiri tira whatu waea mata me te kowiri tira muka sintered ite.
Ko nga rawa o nga papaho taatari matua ko te 304,304L , 316,316L , 904L , Monel , Hastelloy etc.
Āhuatanga:
1.Rahi taapiri nui, Te whanui o te tika o te taatari
2. Te tere porosity, Te pai o te hau rererangi me te ahei o te filtration.
3. He pai te pupuri o te paru, Ohaoha.
4. Te awangawanga o te wera teitei, te aukati i te waikura etc.
5. He maama ngawari, he hangarua.
Whakatakotoranga:
Tere o te whiri: 3-200um
Temperature: -50 ℃ -800 ℃
Diameter: 14-180mm, Roa: 35-1500mm
Kei te waatea hoki te whakarite.
Nga tono:
1) Te umanga polymer teitei
2) Ahumahi Petrochemical
3) Te rongoa me te umanga whakamahine kai
4) Maimoatanga wai
5) Nga miihini me nga umanga kaipuke
6) Whakapai Air
7) Ko etahi atu: Te wera nui, te teitei o te pokuru, te pehanga nui.

I ka North American XB-70 Valkyrie, he prototype supersonic bomber o ka US pō 1950. Ua papahana maʻAmelika'Ākau. ua kūkuluʻia elua wale no kope, kekahi o na mea i lukuia ma ka ulia.
I ka lilo ana o ka prototype kakauinoa i ka make palapala ana o ka papahana. Keia holo ana He holo hoʻolaha, he nui journalists poe hoike i ka ulia i keia loa pipiʻi mīkini, mea kaupaona 250 tons, a ua loaʻa 10 manawa kona kaumaha i loko o ke gula.
ka ulia
Ma ka 8 June 1966, i ka lua o ka prototype lau Edwards Afb e hana ana i ka sonic'iako. Eia hou, ua hōʻike apono 'General uila, Hookah o na kiko'ī XB-70, e kiʻi o ka airplane hoʻolaha me ka F-4B Phantom II, F-104N Starfighter, F-5A ku okoa ana ALOHA, a me ka T -38 Talon, na mana me kiko'ī mai General pila nui. Akā,ʻo ka F-104, hoopukaia ma ke Wake turbulence ua loaʻa ma ka XB-70, luku aku, e luku i ka hema vertical stabilizer. Mahope o 16 kekona o ka holo, ke bomber loaʻa mai loko mai o ka ana, alaila, ili.
Al White, ka XB-70 ke kahu moku, kipaku i ka wa, aka, o kona copilot Carl kea, ua hikiʻole i kēlā kipakuʻana, a ua make, a me ke kahu moku, o ka F-104, Joseph Albert Walker. (Source Wikipedia)

Mayor Pire de Blasio i korerotia i te wiki whakamutunga he $ 28.8 miriona tahua me te whaainga kia tapahia te nama ki te kore i te 2024. ... 
iimatanga o Vision Zero.
Me pehea e mahi ai ratou? Ko te whakaaro matua ko te whakarite i nga rori me nga punaha waka e akiaki ana i nga tikanga taraiwa haumaru i te waa e kore e tau te tangata. Ko te tikanga ka whakahekehia nga rohe tere tere, te raupatu waka aunoa, tae atu ki nga tipu tipu kua whakanohohia ma nga rori o te rohe hei whakahau i nga taraiwa kia tupato. "Me taea e koe te mahi hapa me te kore e whiua e te mate," ko Lars Darin mai i te Tari Whakawhiti Rawa Ka korerotia ki te New Yor
...
e mahere hou o te taone nui ka whakauruhia te kaha (kia rite ki nga kaiwhakamahara pouaka pouaka pango i roto i te takiwa), nga waahanga whakatiki arterial i reira ka heke te rohe tere ki te 25 mph, me te whakauru i nga reiti tere 250 hou.
I tenei ra, @VisionZeroNYC Kei te haere tonu te kaute o te Twitter ki te tuhi i nga mate katoa me nga whara i roto i te taone nui. I te whakaaro ko te kai te whakahou i nga wa maha i ia ra, he nui nga mahi a New York City i mua i te 2024.

Mau ana ngā kanohi ki ngā wāhine o Te Tii i a Ani Taurua e tu rae ki te rae ana kia Titewhai Harawira te wahine kua roa nei e paeārahi ana.
I pakaru mai tēnei take i tēra wiki tonu, i te tono a te Marae ki a Harawira kia heke iho, ahakoa tana aronga kore ki taua tono ko te tūmanako a ētahi kia mahi tahi ngā kuia, kia tutuki ai te kaupapa. Heoi mohio pū ai te whakautu a Harawira i tona taenga atu ki te kēti me te kii” kao e kore tera e mahia e au”.
He tautohe kaore i pirangitia e te Marae, engari no te pupūtanga o te riri ka whakamau atu ngā kanohi a te marea. I ngana a Pita Sharples me ētahi atu ki te whakatau i ngā riri engari auare ake.
I hāere tonu te pakanga mo te ringa o te Pirimia i te Pirimia e tatari ana i tōna waka. Ahakoa te hiahia a Kingi Taurua he tarahiti o te Marae ki te whakamutua i te raru, pai ake kia noho ia ki waho nā te mea i puta te rere i te whiu nga rōpu e rua i ētahi kupu whakaparahako.
I te mutunga iho, kaore rawa tētahi o te tokorua nei mo te heke, no reira i tae mai te Pirimia me tāna menemene, ka kihi i te wahine māro a Titewhai ka whakaeke i te Marae, kaua ko ia me Titewhai anake, engari ko ia me tētahi kāhui tara tokowhā te nui.

- Mai ka hopena o 2012, ua hoʻonui ʻo Kina i kāna waiwai hoʻokomo kālā ma Tibet.
- Ua hoʻouka ka ʻāpana i nā huina mokulele he 130, me nā kūlanakauhale he 61 i pili i nā lele.
- ʻO Lhasa Gonggar Airport ke kahua mokulele nui loa ma Tibet.
ʻO ka kahua mokulele nui loa ma ke komohana hema o Kina Tibet Autonomous Region i hoʻomaka i ka hana i kēia lā, ma hope o ʻekolu mau makahiki o ke kūkulu ʻana.
ʻO ke kikowaena hou o Lhasa Gonggar Airport e like me ka pua lotus mai luna. E kōkua ia i ke kahua mokulele e kū i ka pahuhopu o ka lawelawe ʻana i 9 miliona mau ohua a me 80,000 tone o nā ukana a me nā leka e 2025, e like me ka mokulele.
Aia ma Gonggar County o Shannan City a kokoke i ke kapikala āpana o Lhasa, ʻo Lhasa Gonggar Airport ke kahua mokulele nui loa ma Tibet.
Mai ka hopena o ka makahiki 2012, ua hoʻonui ʻo Kina i kāna waiwai hoʻokomo kālā ma Tibet. Ua hoʻouka ka ʻāpana i nā huina mokulele he 130, me nā kūlanakauhale he 61 i pili i nā lele. ʻO ka helu o nā huakaʻi hele i hana ʻia ma o kēia mau kahua mokulele i 5.18 miliona i 2020.

I takea mai tēnei haki i tērā i mauria e te Māori mai i te tau 1834. I karangatia tērā haki ko te haki ā-motu o Te Whakaminenga o Ngā Hapū o Nu Tireni. I hoahoatia mai tēnei haki i runga i te kaipuke o Tory i tōna hekenga mai ki Aotearoa. I te 30 o Hepetema i te tau 1839 ka whakarewaina te haki ki Pito-one. Ko te karangatanga o William Wakefield mō tēnei haki ko te kara o Niu Tireni. Heoi i muri i te hainatanga o te Tiriti o Waitangi i te tau 1840, ka whakaara a Kāwana William Hobson i te taua ki te whakahauraro i te haki i te 30 o ngā rā o Hune i te tau 1840. Because is generally expressed by ta te mea or no te mea, but if the reference is to an antecedent moving cause the preposition na may be used followed by a relative clause (§ 73).
-

-
